{
  "stem": "11964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am Leokadia Jakobiak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My Jewishness had to be put aside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But before that, I had to do something with my younger sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we knew she could not be on the outside because she had very dark hair and very curly black hair, and she was what the Polish would sniff out immediately as a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Poles had a very good nose, and they were very good informants, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister-- my older sister, and I decided that we are going to dye my younger sister's hair to make her blonde.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to the drugstore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got peroxide, and we burnt her hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was like straw, and her hair fell out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we realized we had to shave her hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that this an episode which was really critical in my younger sister's life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a fortunate coincidence was that somebody that I knew, a former boyfriend of mine, who was wondering about and came back to Warsaw, was also on Polish papers, on Aryan papers, with his wife, who was also Jewish on Polish papers.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she worked in a potato chip factory, and she told me that the potatoes are delivered to her factory by nuns.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The convent has a farm, a potato farm, and they have an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if we can concoct some kind of a story, we can say she-- that our younger sister is an orphan.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took her to the Mother Superior.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told her that she suffered meningitis because in Poland when you suffered from meningitis, your, your head is shaved, and that she lost her memory.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
